@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 09. Supervisor Agent Security & Integrity Model (Advanced implementation)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

rectangle "Input Guard" {
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as Controller
  [SupervisorA2aRequestValidator] as Validator
  [PromptInjectionGuard] as Guard
}

rectangle "Audit & Integrity Guard" {
  [SnapshotVerificationQuery] as Auditor #FDF2E9
  [PlanHashCalculator] as HashGen
}

rectangle "Routing & Invocation Guard" {
  [DefaultA2AInvocationService] as Invoker
  [Circuit Breaker] as CircuitBreaker
}

rectangle "State Integrity" {
  [ExecutionConsistencyCoordinator] as Consistency
  [Redis CAS (WATCH/MULTI/EXEC)] as CAS
}

Controller --> Validator : validate_request
Controller --> Guard : sanitize input
Validator --> Auditor : session_id / task_id / request_params

Auditor --> HashGen : recalculate request_hash\ncompare with frozen_plan_hash
Auditor --> Auditor : Session Ownership Check\nState Version Check (Optimistic Lock)
Auditor --> Auditor : TTL Verification\nPlan Drift Policy (Retired Agent Check)

Invoker --> CircuitBreaker : fail-fast on repeated errors
Invoker --> Auditor : implicit allowlist via routing config

Consistency --> CAS : atomic state transition\nversion increment

note right of Auditor
Advanced Integrity Checks:
- request_hash mismatch -> tamper detected
- frozen_plan_hash mismatch -> drift detected
- resume_token mismatch -> invalid resume
- agent_retired check -> security drift block
end note

note bottom of Consistency
Ensures task execution order and 
prevents double-approval or 
race conditions between workers.
end note
@enduml
